				<p>
					<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="subaudible"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tiripuvaṉaccakkaravattikaḷ maturaiyum pāṇṭiyaṉ muṭittalaiyuṅ koṇṭaruḷiya <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulottuṅkacoḻatevaṟku yāṇṭu Aiñcāvatu tiṭṭaikuṭiyāṉa tirucciṟṟampalaccaruppetimaṅkalattu tirumeṟkoyil Empe
					<lb n="2" break="no"/>rumāṉukku Amutupaṭi Uḷḷiṭṭa viñcaṉaṅkaḷukku tiruviṭaiyāṭṭamāka viṭṭa Ūrāvatu <supplied reason="subaudible"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> pulivalattu Ellaikku meṟkkum <unclear>tu</unclear>kkai <unclear>E</unclear>llaikku vaṭakkum vicaiyamākātevivatikkuk kiḻakkum Ātaṉūr muṭikoṇṭacoḷīccuramuṭaiyār te
					<lb n="3" break="no"/>vatāṉattukku teṟkkum Iṉnāṉkellaiyilum naṭuvupaṭṭa maṇṇinattamum puṉceyum kaḷarum Uḷppaṭa kaṭamaiyum pāṭi<unclear>k</unclear>āva<surplus>l</surplus>lum Iṟaiyiliyāka viṭuvit<unclear>tā</unclear>ṉ kaṭaṉtai Ātittaṉ maṇṭaliyāṉa va<unclear>ṅk</unclear>āramuttaraiyaṉ <supplied reason="subaudible"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
				</p>
				
